item.title: CVE-2023-4799|2023-11-21T08:12:11.739Z -- unknown -- magic%20embeds
item.description: The Magic Embeds WordPress plugin before 3.1.2 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
